column1: Old Hindi Songs - The Golden Era
column9: Old Hindi Songs is a free Mobile App created for iPhone, Android, Windows Mobile. Easily find the best of bollywood song videos sung by the best of the Best Lata Mangeshkar, Mohd Rafi, Asha Bhosle, Mukesh and Kishore Kumar. Hindi songs of 50s, 60s and 70s continue to rule the hindi music. The melodious songs composed by Shankar Jaikishan, Madan Mohan, Ravi, Naushad, S D Burman, R D Burman continues to rule the bollywood music amongst hindi music lovers. Relive the screen presence of Shammi Kapoor, Shashi kapoor, Raj kapoor, Dharmendra, Rajinder Kumar, Joy Mukherjee, Biswajit, Manoj Kumar, Dilip Kumar, Dev Anand, Jitendra, Rajesh Khanna, Nutan, Nargis, Sunil Dutt, Vajyanti Mala, Mala Sinha, Asha Parekh, Meena Kumari, Raj Kumar, Sharmila Tagore, Waheeda Rehman, Babita, Tanuja, Sadhna, Helen, Amitabh, Nanda, Jaya Bhaduri. If you want to watch the best lyrics of bollywood by the greats like Hasrat Jaipuri, Majrooh, Shakeel Badayuni, Neeraj, Sahir Ludhianvi, Kaifi Azmi, Shailendra, Anand Bakshi. Purane Hindi gaane or Sadabahar hindi gaane, whatever you may call them. Hindi songs from bollywood have mesmerized generations over decades. Such is the magic of these legends like Rafi, Lata, Asha, Kishore that be these romantic, sad, fun songs, these have never failed to make people love them even today. thus live the bollywood songs of 50s, 60s and 70s evern after 5 decades. Old Bollywood Hits have entertained generations with absolutely marvelous poetry by Hasrat, Neeraj, Majrooh so beautifully composed by greats like Madan Mohan, Naushad, Shankar Jaikishan, R D Burman, Kalyanji Anandji, Laxmikant Pyarelal. These legends of Bollywood created the most enchanting songs that are popular even after decades. All the tracks are available for public viewing at youtube, thanks to the people who have uploaded these tracks. We are just providing easier discovery and ease of use.

"Coloring Book – Kids Paint" is a educational game that encourages and helps your child to learn, develop and grow in an smart and creative way. In addition to amusing him or her, boost their creativity and entertain them positively collaborates in their growth and development.
This entertaining game allows them to learn to draw, colorize, paint, scribble, decorate, create and beautify very simply, just as they would on a paper, book or magazine, using different options to paint like brushes, crayons or pencils.
Children will be able to display all their creativity by coloring, drawing, painting and decorating their artworks with multiple stamps and graphics.
You and your children will surprise by creating and decorating incredible artworks with funny tricks, creating wonders, magic Kingdoms, stimulating their imagination, filling their minds with fantasy and adventures while reflecting everything in their exciting drawings, which they can share with loved ones and friends by WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter or email, among other options.
Their paintings, real artworkst, which were embellished by them with dedication and work will dazzle and amaze parents, grandparents, uncles and loved ones.
Coloring will give your child great satisfaction in realizing the beautiful things he is capable of doing on his own. It develops its capacity to discover, investigate and memorize. It will create drawings that will be valued by your loved ones stimulating your self-esteem.
This entertainment gives you the opportunity to express your inner world and channel your mood and feelings and giving you as a parent another way to understand them.
The drawings can be saved not only in their memories and dreams, also in the app for editing and continue at any time while they learn.
